{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeInputTagComponentTokensProvider"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"anchor":"overview","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Overview"},{"code":["    \/\/ Define your own provider for tag input component tokens","    \/\/ by inheriting from existing provider","    class CustomInputTagComponentTokensProvider: OrangeThemeInputTagComponentTokensProvider {","","        \/\/ Then override the tag component tokens you want.","","        override var borderRadius: BorderRadiusSemanticToken  { borders.radiusNone }","","        override var colorBgPressed: MultipleColorSemanticTokens { colors.actionPressed }","","        \/\/ ...","    }","","    \/\/ Or define your own provider from scratch","    class CustomInputTagComponentTokensProvider: InputTagComponentTokens {","","        \/\/ And implement maybe hundreds of tokens.","        \/\/ You are allowed to use semantic tokens providers if you want to define values.","    }"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Then, you can give this "},{"code":"CustomInputTagComponentTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" to your own theme implementation:"}]},{"code":["class LocalTheme: OrangeTheme {","","    override init() {","        super.init(inputTag: CustomInputTagComponentTokensProvider())","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"or to an already existing theme for example:"}]},{"code":["    OrangeTheme(inputTag: CustomInputTagComponentTokensProvider())"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"It is also possible to use your own semantic tokens providers for this component tokens providers:"}]},{"code":["    \/\/ Uses by default here:","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeBorderSemanticTokensProvider for borders","    \/\/ - OrangeThemColorSemanticTokensProvider for colors","    let inputTagComponentTokensProvider = OrangeThemeInputTagComponentTokensProvider()","","    \/\/ Or use your own space, size and border semantic tokens providers (or only some)","    let inputTagComponentTokensProvider = OrangeThemeInputTagComponentTokensProvider(","                                            borders: CustomBorderSemanticTokensProvider(),","                                            colors: CustomColorSemanticTokensProvider())"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"type":"aside","name":"Since","style":"note","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"0.17.0","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"kind":"content"}],"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A class which wraps all "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"component  tokens of tag input"}]},{"type":"text","text":" objects like "},{"code":"OUDSInputTag","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This provider should be integrated as a "},{"code":"AllInputTagComponentTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Custom themes can use subclass of "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeInputTagComponentTokensProvider","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" and apply the provider they need."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It implements also the protocol "},{"code":"InputTagComponentTokens","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to expose the component tokens for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"tag inputs"}]},{"type":"text","text":" through any "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Tag inputs"}]},{"type":"text","text":" components tokens are defined with semantic tokens of colors (from "},{"code":"AllColorSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"),"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and borders (from "},{"code":"AllBorderSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":")."}],"relationshipsSections":[{"type":"conformsTo","title":"Conforms To","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/AllInputTagComponentTokensProvider","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/19OUDSTokensComponent08InputTagB6TokensP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/s8CopyableP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/TokensProvider"],"kind":"relationships"}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeInputTagComponentTokensProvider","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"metadata":{"externalID":"s:16OUDSThemesOrange0B36ThemeInputTagComponentTokensProviderC","modules":[{"name":"Theme Orange"}],"roleHeading":"Class","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OrangeThemeInputTagComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeInputTagComponentTokensProvider"}],"title":"OrangeT